== Itabi ry'umwotsi ==[[File:Nicotiana.jpg|thumb|Nicotiana]]
Itabi ni kimwe mu biyobyabwenge banywa cyangwa se basohora umwotsi.

[[Itabi]] rikorwa hifashishishijwe ibibabi ,abahanga mu by'ubuzima bavugako

kurubu hariho ubwoko burenga 70 bw'itabi<ref>https://umutihealth.com/kunywa-itabi/</ref> . mu [[Rwanda]] nahandi kw'Isi.

== Ingaruka z'iterwa n'itabi ==
kunywa itabi byangiza mu buryo bukomeye bitewe nuko umwotsi w'itabi 

habamo ikinyabutabire kitwa [[Itabi|nikotine]],ifite ubushobozi bwo kwangiza 

uturemangingo twubatse [[ubwonko]], ndetse bukangiza ubushobozi bwo gufata 

Abahanga bavugako [[Itabi|nikotine]] ihagarika ubudahangarwa bwo kurema 

uturemangingo dusimbura utwangiritse.<ref>https://agakiza.org/Waruziko-kunywa-itabi-byangiza-ingingo-zose-zubatse-umuntu.html</ref>

Ikindi nuko abanywi b'itabi bigabanyiriza

Inyaka 14 yo kubaho ugereranije n'abatarinywa.

ku banywi [[Igikamba (itabi)|b'itabi]] barimenyereye ntago arikuntu cy'oroshye guhita barireka burundu.

bisaba cyane kuba umuntu afite ubushake bukomeye

bwo kurireka mbere ya byose<ref>https://dusabane.wordpress.com/2017/06/02/waruziko-ushobora-kubona-umuti-utuma-ucika-burundu-ku-itabi-n-urumugi/</ref>

== Kunywera itabi mu ruhame ==


Nyuma y'indwara zikomeye z'ihitana imbaga z'abatuye [[isi]], zirimo ibyorezo n'indwara zidakira nka [[SIDA|Sida]] y'isasira ubuzima n'imbaga y'abatuye [[isi]], ishami ry'umuryango w'abibumbye ryita kubuzima riremezariremezako itabi arikimwe mubiteza abatuye isi kw'ibasirwa n'indwara zikomeye z'ihitana imbaga z'abatuye isi.

Million 6 nibo bapfa bariguze bakarinywa, naho abasanga ibihumbi 890 bicwa n'ingaruka ziterwa  

No guhumeka umwotsi w'itabi rinywewe mu ruhame, nu kuvugako ushobora kwicwa n'ingaruka z'itabi ariko utarinywa, ahubwo bigaterwa nuko w'icaranye n'umuntu uri kurinywa, aba baturage kandi bapfa batarageza kumyaka 70 y'amavuko.<ref>https://isangostar.rw/amakuru/mu-rwanda/article/mu-bushakashatsi-bwakozwe-na-oms</ref>

